msgstr "Loading devices..."

#: booking/templates/booking/iot_sensor_dashboard.html:218
msgid "MQ-9 Gas"
msgstr "MQ-9 Gas"

#: booking/templates/booking/iot_sensor_dashboard.html:219
msgid ""
"一酸化炭素(CO)・可燃性ガスの検知。値が高いほどガス濃度が高く、閾値超過でア"
"ラート通知。"
msgstr ""
"Detects carbon monoxide (CO) and combustible gases. Higher values indicate "
"higher gas concentration. Alerts are triggered when the threshold is "
"exceeded."

#: booking/templates/booking/iot_sensor_dashboard.html:234
msgid "Light"
msgstr "Light"

#: booking/templates/booking/iot_sensor_dashboard.html:235
msgid ""
"照度センサー。室内の明るさをリアルタイム計測。営業時間外の異常な明るさ変化を"
"検知可能。"
msgstr ""
"Light sensor. Measures indoor brightness in real-time. Can detect abnormal "
"brightness changes outside business hours."

#: booking/templates/booking/iot_sensor_dashboard.html:250
msgid "Sound"
msgstr "Sound"

#: booking/templates/booking/iot_sensor_dashboard.html:251
msgid "音量レベルの計測。店舗内の環境音を監視し、異常な騒音や静寂を検知。"
msgstr ""
"Measures sound levels. Monitors ambient noise in the store and detects "
"abnormal noise or silence."

#: booking/templates/booking/iot_sensor_dashboard.html:267
msgid "PIR Motion"
msgstr "PIR Motion"

#: booking/templates/booking/iot_sensor_dashboard.html:270
msgid "静止中"
msgstr "No Motion"

#: booking/templates/booking/iot_sensor_dashboard.html:273
msgid ""
"人感（赤外線動体検知）センサー。人の出入りや在室状況をイベント数で表示。"
msgstr ""
"PIR (passive infrared motion detection) sensor. Displays occupancy and "
"movement as event counts."

